Codeigniter 2.1 配置Doctrine 2.2

Doctrine 官方配置codeigniter http://docs.doctrine-project.org/projects/doctrine-orm/en/2.0.x/cookbook/integrating-with-codeigniter.html
Doctrine console command http://wildlyinaccurate.com/useful-doctrine-2-console-commands/
Doctrine 配置教程bolg http://wildlyinaccurate.com/integrating-doctrine-2-with-codeigniter-2/
本地创建
 Set up git http://help.github.com/mac-set-up-git/
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email ""

Next steps:
  mkdir CI-Doctrine
  cd CI-Doctrine
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:aican0830/CI-Doctrine.git
  git push -u origin master

Existing Git Repo?
  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:aican0830/CI-Doctrine.git
  git push -u origin master
